/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77f6711110f266369ee75aff18b036645051a6d","tid":1577812,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:41:39.000Z","msg":"咁得啦，你可以改定名做黨鐵"},{"pid":"d038a50cfda76ebdbe94455edd5d1a47a4afd065","tid":1577812,"uid":290973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾黨鐵"},{"pid":"2e2217d9473aa8583ccac7f72cfc6e1d9bebcfa0","tid":1577812,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"D鋸㗎佬有無三粒星架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd5d1b58240d669e27101623d547735089ba0f7","tid":1577812,"uid":303830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"嗱，黨鐵係服務d狗架咋，所以炒車想整死香港人係佢地兌現緊佢地嘅承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f323d6dd560d6f3d9a7e980b194e52c8decb5a","tid":1577812,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"黨鐵: <br />\n為提升安全質素如有需要會要求乘客乘坐前簽生死狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會透過解說和做好服務，爭取股東政府和管理層信任以確保盈利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35ceb4ffcfcd8b48533a298f4d383a27df8ecfa","tid":1577812,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJ6JC8T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJ6JC8T.jpg&h=a6b510fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rci0Fnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frci0Fnd.jpg&h=23b3ebb5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8izKOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8izKOU.jpg&h=b6b650d3&s={